name: AexolGL-js
tagline: Fastest lightest webgl engine. Free 3d game engine!
body:
# Free 3d game engine
AexolGL-js is a game engine, a framework for 3d rendering and game development for JavaScript. AexolGL-js is Open Source and free for any purpose, including commercial ventures & indie developers. To learn how to use AexolGL-js, check live examples and documentation resources.
